It was a heartbreaking Mother's Day weekend for Steve Carell.
The Office star's mother, Harriet Theresa Carell, died at age 90 on Saturday.
"Harriet Theresa Carell.
October 15, 1925- May 7, 2016.
Love You Mom," the 53-year-old actor shared to Twitter on Sunday.
Carell also retweeted a picture remembering his mom.
Acton Funeral Home director Kathleen Boyle says Carell's mother died in her Acton, Massachusetts home, surrounded by family, according to the Associated Press.
